                Founded 2024 by <strong style="color:var(--text);">Pradeep Pandey</strong>. Early-stage, actively
                onboarding Texas CAH pilot partners.
              </p>
              <div class="rule" style="margin:0;"></div>
              <p style="font-size:12px; color:var(--muted); line-height:1.6;">
                Pilot designed to demonstrate measurable time savings within the first two scheduling cycles.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- S9: CTA -->
        <section class="slide" id="s9">
          <div class="s9-left">
            <div class="eyebrow">The Ask</div>
            <h2>Let's Put<br /><span class="accent">AI To Work</span><br />In Your Hospital.</h2>
            <div class="sub" style="margin-top:24px;">
              Join the free 60-day pilot — no contract, no IT project, no risk. Or reach out to discuss the investment
              opportunity.
            </div>
            <a
              href="mailto:hello@simplescheduleai.com"
              style="display:inline-block; margin-top:28px; font-size:18px; font-weight:800; color:var(--accent); text-decoration:none; letter-spacing:-0.01em;"
              >hello@simplescheduleai.com</a
            >
            <div style="margin-top:12px; font-size:12px; color:var(--muted); letter-spacing:0.05em;">
              simplescheduleai.com · Texas · CAH-built · Pilot open now
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="s9-right">
            <div>
              <div class="s9-rh">For Hospital Admins</div>
              <div class="s9-rl">Free 60-day pilot. Your nurses get schedules as always — we handle the rest.</div>
            </div>
            <div style="height:1px; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.15);"></div>
            <div>
              <div class="s9-rh">For Investors</div>
              <div class="s9-rl">Category-defining managed service. 1,300+ CAHs. No real competition.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="s9-url">simplescheduleai.com/pilot</div>
